            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>@SharedLocalizer["Identifying details"].Value </td>
                <td>@SharedLocalizer["Your name and, possibly, in the event of the patient suffering an adverse reaction, contact details"].Value </td>
                <td>@SharedLocalizer["The data you provide to the patient’s prescriber will be passed to the organisation."].Value </td>
                <td>@SharedLocalizer["To enable patient for whom you are responsible to participate in the Cidofovir Exposure Study"].Value </td>
                <td>@SharedLocalizer["Article 6 (1) (f) – it is in the organisation’s legitimate interests to retain information about you for the purpose of recording the consent you give on behalf of a patient to participation in the Cidofovir Exposure Study.The personal data will be kept confidential with access limited to the organisation’s staff who work on the study, or support them. It will not be used for any purpose other than that listed under ‘Why data is processed’. On balance, the organisation’s legitimate interests are not overridden by your interests or fundamental rights and freedoms which require protection of personal data."].Value </td>
